{"tid":763984,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"貝依霖疑似走光露乳暈 網民指博上位：特登露？","createTime":"2018-08-01T14:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T19:15:10.000Z","uid":147522,"like":12,"dislike":334,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"b2128ffd679f32895eb6b8a4aa7f92d7ecec7968","tid":763984,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"自從杜汶澤升呢做老闆後，就不斷為自己新公司甚至自己聘請有樣有身材的員工，繼24歲的後，近日再請多一個私人女秒書莊端兒。不過，最近有傳指貝依霖為求上位，而爆出疑似露乳暈事件！<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤呢排又再聘請一位擁有導彈級身材嘅莊端兒做私人女秘書，同時亦會喺全新資訊性live節目《壹鳩大事回顧》中出現。當時，杜汶澤仲驚自己老婆阿田會對呢位新秘書有意見，皆因莊端兒名副其實係個double may！<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，貝依霖可能眼見勢色唔對路，於是最近就出招為自己喺老闆杜汶澤心入面搶番啲分，嚟招露點點！從相中可見，貝依霖疑似露乳暈！  <br />\n<br />\n結果，相一出就引嚟唔少網民嘅注意及紛紛留言，而貝依霖就澄清自己冇露暈，只係個bra嘅lace，指大家誤會咗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/224708_6cd63d9474854988e1afcdccbdaa76a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F224708_6cd63d9474854988e1afcdccbdaa76a3.png&h=6290329b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fdf69aebce8abf6ada53abea2834808859bb3a6","tid":763984,"uid":193488,"like":393,"dislike":2,"score":391,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:48:41.000Z","msg":"原圖？老母？"},{"pid":"85498cb839a35f7316abf1123db697bf8dccb9fa","tid":763984,"uid":91664,"like":251,"dislike":2,"score":249,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇原圖出乜撚post"},{"pid":"471b893346d5ecfada32d3dcb9804f508a4a9235","tid":763984,"uid":62384,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:50:36.000Z","msg":"我睇咗d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59b649d1f0959382aaabd7741a3a7abc2b0e6d4","tid":763984,"uid":24443,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T14:51:29.000Z","msg":"吊你老母 你比依張圖我睇把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"01a0a776da4e7a1fc5ed4216f90db05208448676","tid":7